          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 17</h1><p><strong>Questions 11 - 15</strong></p><p>Choose the correct letter, <strong>A, B or C</strong>.</p><p>11 Which methods of promotion did Janet use as a means to advertise the speech?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    The radio and posters</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    Posters and e-mail</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    E-mail and the radio</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>12 What was the reason that Janet met Mr Mwanza in Mpanda?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    Travel problems.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    They met by accident at the bus station.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    They sat next to each other on a bus.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>13 How long did Janet first spend in Mpanda?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    1 night</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    2 weeks</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    1 year</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>14 What is the age range of the girls in the class?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    12 - 16</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    12 - 17</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    16 - 17</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>15 What other service does the school often have to provide the students in addition to education?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    Accommodation</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    Travel expenses</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    Transport from their homes to the school</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>",
